    "Name": "Hunchback",
    "Details": "Lukas \"Locke\" Laramie's personal modification of an HBK-4G, built around a Clan-sourced Ultra AC/20 with a remarkable seven tons of ammunition. The sustained fire capability consistently surprises opponents who expect a standard Hunchback to run dry far sooner. Original Medium Lasers and a Small Laser remain as backup. Clan double heat sinks keep the main gun cycling reliably through extended engagements.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>",
